    <string name="bt_no_paired">No paired devices</string>
    <string name="bt_how_to_pair_info"><![CDATA[<html>You need to pair this device with another device running %1$s to be able to mirror the scoreboard screen.
    Typically this is done by performing steps along the way of:
<ul>
    <li>on both devices, open the bluetooth settings screen</li>
    <li>ensure that on the target device
        <ul>
            <li>bluetooth is turned \'On\'</li>
            <li>the device is (temporary) visible to other devices</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li>on this device select \'Pair new device\'</li>
    <li>the target device should show up under \'Available Devices\': select it</li>
    <li>Confirm the pairing on both devices</li>
</ul>
</html>]]></string>

